des:
Disclaimer: This skill calls an AI-generated parody of Kanye!

Now you can speak to a virtual Kanye through your Alexa device. 

Kanye will interact with you (with your name or any name you give), answer your questions and much more. Ask things like tell me a joke, read Twitter, tell you facts, how are you, the border wall, Poopity Scoop and more!
